[The mentioned new inactivated rabies vaccine is likely to be the one addressed in the following recent paper:
Balashov AN, Doronin MI, Borisov AV, et al. Studies on humoral immunity in dogs after use of rabies inactivated vaccines formulated with Montanide ISA 70 VG and GEL 01 adjuvants. Veterinariia Segodnia (Veterinary Science Today) 2020; (1): 25-30 (in Russian); https://veterinary.arriah.ru/jour/article/view/454#1/ (abstract in English). - Mod.AS

